name: Advanced Laboratory in Human Biology
description: Building on their experience in 3rd-year labs, students participate in inquiry-based laboratory experiments in diverse areas of current human biology research. Open to students in any Human Biology program. Please see Human Biology Program Website for subtopic details, which vary from year to year. (Lab Materials Fee: $51)
prerequisites: 14 FCE complete, HMB310H1/ HMB311H1/ HMB312H1/ HMB314H1
